00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:11,520
Let's have crazy fun!

224
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:13,540
Yay!

225
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:15,240
One, two, three, four!

226
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:19,030
♪  We are soulmates   ♪

227
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:22,330
♪   No one will separate us   ♪

228
00:17:22,330 --> 00:17:25,890
♪  We're going to sing joyfully   ♪

