00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:37,770
Woo!

232
00:17:37,770 --> 00:17:40,450
♪  All for you   ♪

233
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:45,030
♪  We made it!   ♪

234
00:17:45,030 --> 00:17:50,140
 You are not someone who deserves to be cheated on by their boyfriend.

235
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:54,600
 You are someone who changes the lives of others.

236
00:17:59,170 --> 00:18:00,760
Bam!

237
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:12,540
 I don't have confidence.

238
00:18:12,540 --> 00:18:16,930
 I can't fix a patient with just confidence.

