00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,750
Hey, hey! Hey!

248
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:03,500
Hey!

249
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:08,350
Hey, you!

250
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:17,130
 Ru Oh, unlike other patients with schizophrenia, knows that he is hallucinating.

251
00:20:17,130 --> 00:20:19,840
 He also knows he is sick.

252
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:23,550
 He also knows that he must take medication.

253
00:20:23,550 --> 00:20:28,240
